---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../../css/services.css";
---

<Layout
  title="Mobile App Development | GeneralSoft UAE"
  description="Professional mobile app development services in the UAE. We build native and cross-platform iOS and Android applications for businesses across all industries."
  path="/services/mobile-apps/"
  image="/img/og-mobile.jpg"
>
  <section class="service-content" id="mobile-services">
    <div class="service-section" style="margin-top: 120px;">
      <h2 class="service-title">Mobile Applications</h2>
      <p>
        Mobile applications have become essential tools for businesses to engage with customers, streamline 
        operations, and drive growth. At GeneralSoft, we develop high-quality mobile applications for iOS 
        and Android platforms that deliver exceptional user experiences and robust performance.
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether you need a customer-facing app to boost engagement, an internal tool to improve team productivity, 
        or a cross-platform solution that reaches users on any device, our mobile development team has the 
        expertise to bring your vision to life.
      </p>

      <h3>Our Mobile Development Services</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Native iOS Development</h4>
          <p>Swift and SwiftUI applications optimized for iPhone and iPad with full access to Apple's ecosystem features.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Native Android Development</h4>
          <p>Kotlin and Jetpack Compose applications designed for the Android platform with Material Design guidelines.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Cross-Platform Development</h4>
          <p>Flutter and React Native applications that run on both iOS and Android from a single codebase, reducing time and cost.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>App Maintenance & Support</h4>
          <p>Ongoing maintenance, updates, performance optimization, and feature enhancements for your mobile applications.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Our Mobile Tech Stack</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>iOS: Swift, SwiftUI, UIKit, Combine</li>
        <li>Android: Kotlin, Jetpack Compose, Material Design</li>
        <li>Cross-Platform: Flutter, React Native</li>
        <li>Backend: Firebase, Node.js, AWS Amplify</li>
        <li>Testing: XCTest, Espresso, Detox</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Projects Proof Section -->
      <div class="projects-proof">
        <h3>Proven Mobile Delivery — Projects Completed</h3>
        <p>
          Our mobile portfolio includes consumer apps, enterprise mobility
          solutions, and IoT-connected applications deployed in production.
        </p>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Recycling App with AI Object Recognition</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Apr 2023 – Aug 2023</span>
            <span class="role">Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Developed a cross-platform mobile application (Android and iPhone)
            that uses AI-powered real-time object recognition to identify and
            classify recyclable materials. Users point their camera at an item
            and the app instantly identifies the material type, provides
            recycling instructions, and locates nearby recycling centers. Built
            with Flutter, Firebase, and integrated IoT sensors for smart bin
            connectivity.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">Flutter</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Firebase</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">AI</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Real-Time Object Recognition</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">IoT</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Android</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">iOS</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>App For Hygiene Service Providers</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Sep 2021 – Dec 2022</span>
            <span class="role">Media Consultant & Trainer. Web & App Developer.</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Developed a cross-platform mobile application for hygiene service
            providers in Abu Dhabi. Built with Flutter and a microservices
            backend architecture. The app manages service scheduling, customer
            management, real-time service tracking, and payment processing.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">Flutter</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Microservices</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Firebase</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Android</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">iOS</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Mobile Application for Acute Healthcare — Germany</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Jul 2005 – Aug 2005</span>
            <span class="role">Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Developed a mobile application for acute healthcare in Germany using
            C++, BizTalk Messaging, and BizTalk Orchestration. The application
            processed inbound data including flat files and EDI documents with
            attachments. Wrote a custom BizTalk DICOM adapter for medical
            imaging integration. Used GIS location information for activating
            and routing healthcare response algorithms.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">C++</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">BizTalk</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">DICOM</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">EDI</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">GIS</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Healthcare</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Corporate Store Apps — Windows Phone & RT</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Oct 2014 – Jan 2015</span>
            <span class="role">Architect & Lead Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Built corporate store applications for Windows Phone and Windows RT
            as part of an enterprise ERP migration project. The apps provided
            mobile access to inventory, order management, and business
            analytics. Integrated with Azure AD for secure authentication and
            on-premises backend systems.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">Windows Phone</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Windows RT</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Azure</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">BizTalk</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">SAP</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faq-section">

    <div class="container">
      <div class="faq-container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Common questions about our mobile app development services.</p>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <details>
            <summary>Should I build a native or cross-platform app?</summary>
            <p>It depends on your requirements. Native apps offer the best performance and access to device features. Cross-platform apps are more cost-effective and faster to develop. We'll help you choose the right approach.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary>How long does mobile app development take?</summary>
            <p>A standard mobile app typically takes 8–16 weeks for development. Complex apps with advanced features like real-time sync, AI integration, or IoT connectivity may take longer.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary>Do you publish apps to the App Store and Google Play?</summary>
            <p>Yes. We handle the entire app store submission process, including preparing screenshots, descriptions, and ensuring compliance with store guidelines.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-content">
        <h2>Build Your Mobile App</h2>
        <p>Ready to create a mobile app for your business? Contact our development team to discuss your project.</p>
        <div class="contact-info">
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="contact-item-icon">🌐</div><strong>Website</strong><a href="https://generalsoft.ae">generalsoft.ae</a>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <a href="/en/contact/"><div class="contact-item-icon">📧</div><strong>Contact Us</strong><br />Get in touch</a>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="contact-item-icon">📍</div><strong>Location</strong><span>Ras Al Khaimah</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
